title: [Sturmgren's Outfitting]
[Sturmgren's General Store]
[Sturmgren's Magic Shoppe]
description: The broad sweep of the mahogany floor is interrupted by a serene golden wyvern fountain.  Halfway to the arched ceiling, a tattered merchant permit hangs on one of the colorful brocade walls.  A twisted dark metal rack and a carved oak table are pushed close together in the back of the shop.
